1. The package includes 
    |-              Makefile, start.S, Flowchart_of_ROMbootloader.jpg, Flowchart_of_Bootloader8K.jpg
    |- bsp:         BSP, main ,
    |- drivers:     nandc, sdc, sdc_cntr, scu, serial
    |- lib:         mini ANSI C library

2. Modify bsp/config.mk to decide text base address of linker (-Ttext), 
   ex. use BIN with 0x00000000, use ELF with 0x00008000

3. use 'make' to build rom_bl.bin or rom_bl.elf

